data.description: "Welcome to your dream home! This captivating 3-bedroom luxury residence can be yours, situated just moments away from DHR, Edinburg Regional Hospital, Cinemark Bistro, and Bert Ogden Arena.   Enjoy elegance and functionality with an open-concept layout that seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living areas. The high ceilings enhance the spacious feel, creating an ideal space for entertaining friends and family. The kitchen is equipped with sleek stainless steel appliances, stunning quartz countertops, spacious cabinets and a great walk-in pantry.  The thoughtfully designed outdoor living space is tailor-made for hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet evenings.   This home goes above and beyond with a versatile bonus room. It's perfect for a work-from-home setup, personal gym, or a comfortable 4th bedroom. Summerset Estates is a community known for its family-friendly atmosphere. Schedule your exclusive private showing today and make this magnificent home yours!"
